snippet: Stephen Curry screamed, turned and kicked the nearby wall, disgusted by another missed jumper. It was just practice and most of his other shots went in, so there was little reason for concern....

headline.main: Washington Receiver John Ross Breaks NFL Combine's 40 Record
headline.print_headline: Washington Receiver John Ross Breaks NFL Combine's 40 Record

lead_paragraph: Stephen Curry screamed, turned and kicked the nearby wall, disgusted by another missed jumper. It was just practice and most of his other shots went in, so there was little reason for concern.
